rrior over other warriors?<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/udinadian.showPublicProfile?language=EN>dinadian</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/3/01 1:24:05 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Ogre stun protection</span><hr size=1> Well,  they can't be stunned by any melee attack from the front.  Even at low levels when tanking against skels or madmen you can get stunned resulting in a potential loss of an attack for you.  I suppose that this would be most useful against warrior type MOBs or dueling someone that can bash, slam or stunkick.  The funny thing is that a lot of ogres don't even realize the have this capacity which indicates that some chnge in tactics are indicated in order to make the best use of it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/utugorisfat.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tugor is fat</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 43<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/4/01 9:57:27 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://facelink.com/K95152?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Ogre stun protection</span><hr size=1> It's pretty good for dueling.  I was dueling (stood in front of each other and traded hits) a level 60 Troll Warrior with almost full beserkers, CoCW, and some exquisite velium weapons vs my 1044 self buffed AC and Lam+Club of the Ice Ocean combo... got him down to half a bub when he finally killed me because I stunned him so much while he couldn't stun me =P  Other than that, it just lets you do more damage because you aren't getting stunned fighting a mob.<br>
<br>
-Tugor <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=nubb>Nubb</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/01 8:27:43 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Ogre stun protection</span><hr size=1> It can be an advantage when pulling, particularly when sow'd. I typically pull running backwards, while attempting to slam the target. Never get stunned and do a little damage on occasion with melee/slam/riposte while luring the critter to my waiting friends. Plus it helps keep the critter mad at me, the tank, when the real fray begins.<br>
<br>
It also can be a life saver.. backing into the zone with a horde chasing you means you're not going to do the spinning dance of death.<br>
<br>
Nubb <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessage?topicID=324.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessage?topicID=288.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.emailToFriend?topicID=306.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.threadControl?topicID=306.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=306.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=306.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub14.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesteelwarriorthearena">The Arena<option value="thesteelwarriorthebattlefield">The BattleField<option value="thesteelwarriorthebunker">The Bunker<option value="thesteelwarriorthetavern">The Tavern<option value="thesteelwarriorfrm6">The Keep</select></td><td><input type=submit value="Go" class=inputbutton></td></tr></table></form></td></tr></table><br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior>The S